{
  "stem": "27770.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then at fourth gymnasium, they united the boys and the girls in gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Hebrew gymnasium was in a high level.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And to explain it to you why, we had next to Munkatsh, another 40 kilometer, another town, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was also having a Hebrew gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I would say, from the whole study, of what they studied there, was altogether maybe 10% or 15% in Hebrew, the rest was in Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In our Hebrew school, 90% you can say was in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Physic, we learned in Hebrew language, history in Hebrew language.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Math, we learned in Hebrew language.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they were concentrated, really, to talk just Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We Had in the school, in Hebrew gymnasium, uniform hats.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Each hat has an emblem, what-- like a Ten Commandments pin on it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we had also some rim.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It means guards.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If we were, in the morning, in the school, afternoon, they used to be on the street and watching the students, who is talking Hebrew?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We supposed to talk only Hebrew and not the Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If any boy or girl, they catched who is not talking Hebrew, they just mark down their name.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And next day, we have to pay in a few pennies fine, because we didn't spoke Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We spoke Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that's how we learned the language so good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I arrived, in Israel, in 1949, my Hebrew just as fluently as a Sabra who was born in Israel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And what language did you speak in the home, amongst yourselves, with the family?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We started to speak in my parents' Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then, later on, I spoke Hungarian, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because that was the official language.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't remember the Czechish language, because at this time, I didn't-- I was never in a Czechish school.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
